companyName: Invesco S&P International Developed Low Volatility
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results (before fees and expenses) of the S&P BMI International Developed Low VolatilityTM Index (the "underlying index").
 The fund will invest at least 90% of its total assets in the securities of companies that comprise the underlying index. S&P Dow Jones Indices ("S&P DJI" or the "index provider") compiles, maintains and calculates the underlying index, which is designed to measure the performance of 200 of the least volatile stocks of the S&P Developed ex-U.S. & South Korea LargeMidCap Index.
